[normal]Annex 1[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]About WRAP[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]37.
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]WRAP 
[normal](the Waste &amp; Resources Action Programme) 
[normal]is an independent, not-for-profit company, recognised in the UK and internationally for our expertise in resource efficiency and product sustainability, our leading-edge evidence, our skills and knowledge and our ability to bring people together to solve problems.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]38.
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]WRAP’s vision is
[normal]:
[normal] 
[normal]‘A
[normal] world where resources are used sustainably.
[normal]’
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]39.
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]We occupy a unique space as a trusted interface between Governments, business, communities and organisations working for more sustainable resources.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]40.
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]WRAP acts as a catalyst, accelerating change in the behaviour of business and communities in ways that neither governments nor individual companies can 
[normal]do, 
[normal]working on their own.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]41.
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]We do this through a combination of:
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]42.
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Our delivery is based on carefully building and understanding the evidence base, then working with partners to address the market failures that prevent the sustainable use of resources.  Tackling these, in the right order and cost effectively, is essential to effective market operation and is at the h
[normal]eart of the way WRAP operates.
